      • addSessionData

        public void addSessionData(String key,
                           String value)
        Add session data
        Specified by:
        addSessionData in interface org.fcrepo.kernel.api.FedoraSession
        Parameters:
        key - the data key
        value - the data value Note: while the FedoraSession interface permits multi-valued session data, this implementation constrains that to be single-valued. That is, calling obj.addSessionData("key", "value1") followed by obj.addSessionData("key", "value2") will result in only "value2" being associated with the given key.
